    ('白开水', 'báikāishuǐ', 'nước lọc', '请给我一杯白开水，谢谢。', 'Qǐng gěi wǒ yī bēi báikāishuǐ, xièxiè.', 'Làm ơn cho tôi một cốc nước lọc, cảm ơn.', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-ce1cccbc2eb31187ea57254a.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-1d084b9225a0437f0a3f8d52.mp3', 181),
    ('打包', 'dǎbāo', 'mang về, đóng gói mang về', '这份菜太多了，可以帮我打包吗？', 'Zhè fèn cài tài duō le, kěyǐ bāng wǒ dǎbāo ma?', 'Món này quá nhiều, xin giúp tôi đóng gói mang về được không?', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-a9a49c817394f8e96f3c6ca6.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-78f2c68ee3944f0198b8c07a.mp3', 182),
    ('外卖', 'wàimài', 'giao đồ ăn, đồ mang về', '你们这里有外卖服务吗？我想订一份晚餐。', 'Nǐmen zhèlǐ yǒu wàimài fúwù ma? Wǒ xiǎng dìng yī fèn wǎncān.', 'Quán có dịch vụ giao hàng không? Tôi muốn đặt một phần bữa tối.', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-f42db5493d75fdb3ec943465.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-2afd98cf7145ae48f68a90ba.mp3', 183),
    ('账单', 'zhàngdān', 'hóa đơn', '请帮我结账，麻烦把账单拿过来。', 'Qǐng bāng wǒ jiézhàng, máfan bǎ zhàngdān ná guòlái.', 'Làm ơn giúp tôi thanh toán, phiền lấy hóa đơn ra.', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-4bf3c13e5809517f7365762a.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-d96201939ae520b4c5a4ea6d.mp3', 184),
