    ('付款', 'fùkuǎn', 'thanh toán', '可以用刷卡付款吗？', 'Kěyǐ yòng shuākǎ fùkuǎn ma?', 'Có thể thanh toán bằng thẻ không?', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-6f0546de73d1c9b069354a3e.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-7d5fb524c30f2519d11e49ea.mp3', 186),
    ('小费', 'xiǎofèi', 'tiền boa', '服务很好，我准备给服务员一点小费。', 'Fúwù hěn hǎo, wǒ zhǔnbèi gěi fúwùyuán yīdiǎn xiǎofèi.', 'Dịch vụ rất tốt, tôi chuẩn bị cho nhân viên một chút tiền boa.', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-6ecc66d161c3677ba55ffe91.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-dcd42bcfef0cbbf58215bbe7.mp3', 187),
    ('投诉', 'tóusù', 'phàn nàn', '我想投诉，菜上错了还有点凉。', 'Wǒ xiǎng tóusù, cài shàng cuò le hái yǒu diǎn liáng.', 'Tôi muốn phàn nàn, món ăn lên nhầm mà còn hơi nguội.', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/word-819ed55cb7159b1c1fb54a27.mp3', 'https://ssmqppvkgffknfqdvpwg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/card-audio/templates/am-thuc-goi-mon-200/sentence-48b813200c49600f93c27bd3.mp3', 188),
